'''精神益生菌'''（{{lang-en|'''Psychobiotics'''}}）是指一些可能對[[心理健康|心理健康]]有益的[[益生菌|益生菌]]，其作用機制可能是在人們適量服用後，透過調整宿主{{link-en|微生物群相|microbiota}}來達到。目前已在進行相關的前期研究<ref name="Sarkar_2016" />。有關細菌對[[腸—腦軸線|腸—腦軸線]]是否有影響，是目前研究的主題之一。不過，到2018年為止，還沒有[[随机对照试验|随机对照试验]]可以確認服用菌株後對心理健康的明確影響，而目前已經完成的實驗，在整體評估上的結論還不確定<ref name="romijn">{{cite journal | vauthors = Romijn AR, Rucklidge JJ | title = Systematic review of evidence to support the theory of psychobiotics | journal = Nutrition Reviews | volume = 73 | issue = 10 | pages = 675–93 | date = October 2015 | pmid = 26370263 | doi = 10.1093/nutrit/nuv025 | doi-access = free }}</ref><ref name="lin">{{cite journal | vauthors = Liu B, He Y, Wang M, Liu J, Ju Y, Zhang Y, Liu T, Li L, Li Q | title = Efficacy of probiotics on anxiety-A meta-analysis of randomized controlled trials | journal = Depression and Anxiety | volume = 35 | issue = 10 | pages = 935–45 | date = July 2018 | pmid = 29995348 | doi = 10.1002/da.22811| s2cid = 51615532 }}</ref>。

== 種類 ==
[[File:Fructans.svg|thumb]]
在進行精神益生菌的相關研究時，最常使用的細菌是[[革蘭氏陽性菌|革蘭氏陽性菌]]，例如[[双歧杆菌属|双歧杆菌属]]及[[乳桿菌屬|乳桿菌屬]]，其中不含[[脂多糖|脂多糖]]鏈，可以減少[[免疫應答|免疫應答]]的可能性<ref name="Sarkar_2016">{{cite journal | vauthors = Sarkar A, Lehto SM, Harty S, Dinan TG, Cryan JF, Burnet PW | title = Psychobiotics and the Manipulation of Bacteria-Gut-Brain Signals | journal = Trends in Neurosciences | volume = 39 | issue = 11 | pages = 763–81 | date = November 2016 | pmid = 27793434 | pmc = 5102282 | doi = 10.1016/j.tins.2016.09.002 }}</ref>。[[益生元|益生元]]（Prebiotics）是可以幫助對人體有益[[微生物|微生物]]（例如在腸道內[[发酵|发酵]]的細菌）活動或是成長的物質，例如[[果聚糖|果聚糖]]，[[寡醣|寡醣]]）<ref name="Sarkar_2016" /><ref name="2015defRev">{{cite journal | vauthors = Hutkins RW, Krumbeck JA, Bindels LB, Cani PD, Fahey G, Goh YJ, Hamaker B, Martens EC, Mills DA, Rastal RA, Vaughan E, Sanders ME | title = Prebiotics: why definitions matter | journal = Current Opinion in Biotechnology | volume = 37 | pages = 1–7 | date = February 2016 | pmid = 26431716 | pmc = 4744122 | doi = 10.1016/j.copbio.2015.09.001 }}</ref>。若在單一益生菌培養基中產生的多種菌種，會稱為polybiotic<ref name=":5">{{cite journal | vauthors = Bambury A, Sandhu K, Cryan JF, Dinan TG | title = Finding the needle in the haystack: systematic identification of psychobiotics | journal = British Journal of Pharmacology | volume = 175 | issue = 24 | pages = 4430–38 | date = December 2018 | pmid = 29243233 | pmc = 6255950 | doi = 10.1111/bph.14127 }}</ref>。

== 研究 ==
2021年針對用精神益生菌治療青年人的焦慮，沒有顯著的效果<ref name="cohen">{{Cite journal|last=Cohen Kadosh|first=Kathrin|last2=Basso|first2=Melissa|last3=Knytl|first3=Paul|last4=Johnstone|first4=Nicola|last5=Lau|first5=Jennifer Y. F.|last6=Gibson|first6=Glenn R.|date=2021-06-16|title=Psychobiotic interventions for anxiety in young people: a systematic review and meta-analysis, with youth consultation|journal=Translational Psychiatry|language=en|volume=11|issue=1|pages=1–12|doi=10.1038/s41398-021-01422-7|issn=2158-3188|pmc=8206413|pmid=34131108}}</ref>。因為目前的研究還有一些例外的結果，還需要更多樣性的人體研究<ref name=romijn/><ref name=lin/><ref name=cohen/>。

